social_posts.post_text: Apologies if it’s too graphic. “You Won’t” link in bio. Let me know your favorite line.

I do really appreciate the reception to the new video. It’s been years since I dropped or posted anything but not for a second did I stop creating; I actually started creating more in that time. Being labeled a Warlord, having people put things on my name that I would never do, having people try to assassinate me physically and my character has been a rollercoaster that started off as eye opening, then hurtful, exhausting, and many other feelings in between but the major feeling I’ve been left with is a breath of fresh air & new beginnings. In all this time I’ve realized how much I don’t give a fck what any of you think at all, respectfully 😂 I love y’all but I could care less. Me being off social media for so long really proved that to myself. I just didn’t really realize how many fcks I didn’t give. If you don’t know me, never known me yet you’re weighing in negatively on my character it means absolutely nothing. The fact that my mom knows who I am & is proud, close friends and family, people who were around these situations/ accusations and know what the media & others have said about me isn’t true because they were there, that’s what means something to me & has helped keep me grounded with an ounce of sanity- because there were definitely moments I felt I was in the twilight zone. For a while in my past years of my silence I had this feeling of a type of ego death where I felt there’s no need for me to release any of this music because I’m not any more special than any other human. If I don’t release music there’s millions of other artists fans can listen to. It felt like a level of humility I was comfortable with sitting in. It wasn’t till more recently that I realized that feeling of “humility” 🤮 was not humility at all. It was complacency. That’s when I realized I had to get up, out, knock it all the way off and cut the silence. Everything the media did was to silence me so me being silent was giving them exactly what they wanted because all the while they could paint me however they wanted, fill in the blanks I left for them & use me as an example to preemptively silence any young folks who felt they had a voice & want change. No more tho we outside.

We should be able to disagree and still be cool. I like having friends that think differently. Now when people don’t agree with each other they act like they’re enemies, all on social media spewing hate towards each other. Wild.

This one has me a little f’d up cuz it’s so close to home. RIP to @lavishrich_206 bro really had a good spirit. I’d seen lots of growth in him, maturing, tryna keep good energy with others round the town and beyond. Hearing they got him over some jealousy and them not being thorough is a tragedy. I decided to drop this video today for bro cuz when I saw him last, a couple weeks back it was on the back street where he just got shot and I introduced him to my son and he was talkin bout rockin wit my new video that dropped. It’s disgusting to see another one of us taken away for nothing, so senselessly. 

On the other side of the spectrum… the main character in this video @4lptsd passed away a couple months back and we were not cool before his passing. I was tracking him down myself to have a few choice words with him. It’s ironic because what transpired between us was so similar to the plot of the video. Staying out the way from snakes, set ups and general betrayal. I still don’t Fuck wit dog cuz I have to keep it real, death or not.  But I do wish the best for his daughter, babies mom, family and friends. I think his soul was better than the shell of a man he was when he passed. He was fighting some demons and those will tear your family apart and forever scar your loved ones, especially lil ones. I wish them peace and a less rocky future.

I can’t not speak up about this. And me being me I’m not going to sugar coat it the way others do to make sure they don’t get canceled. I couldn’t care less about cancellation. Wrong is wrong. Fuck the terrorist Israeli government. They remind me more of the Nazi regime than just about anything I’ve ever seen in my short lifetime.
This is Israel’s CURRENT prime minister now….. the guy who essentially had the former prime minister assassinated through inciting violent, hateful, bigoted riots because him and his party, who is in power today, did not want Israel to make peace with Palestine(and the former prime minister was working on doing just that and being effective at it). The current prime minister and his party wanted to continue genociding the Palestinians. That was in 1995!……. The current prime minister is the longest-tenured prime minister in Israel’s entire history… sound familiar? If he isn’t Hitler reincarnated I don’t know what. He’s also one of the only Israeli prime ministers to actually be born in Israel… the majority of Israel’s prime ministers were Russian, born in Russia.

I don’t understand how people are on a fence about this. The only answer I can come up with is simply most not being informed, being misinformed or more likely a mixture of the two. So here’s a quick synopsis. 
This IS NOT a “choose a side” Israelis vs Palestinians or Jews vs Muslims… thats ridiculous for one, but it’s also a bastardization and minimization of what’s actually occurring. The scale of it, the breadth of evil, the chess that’s been played with lives to get to this point and for how long these war crimes and atrocities have gone unchecked and unchallenged.
